  {%- comment -%} 14a. Image optimization for 4G networks {%- endcomment -%}
  {%- comment -%}
    Image Loading Best Practices for 4G Performance:
    1. Logo uses eager loading + high fetchpriority + WebP/AVIF support
    2. Hero images use fetchpriority="high" with responsive formats
    3. Collection icons use eager loading for first 4 + WebP/AVIF
    4. Product images on PDP use lazy loading with decoding="async"
    5. All images include explicit width/height to prevent CLS
    6. Picture elements provide AVIF > WebP > original format fallback
